         <abstract id="aspace_aa02d5a3af7fcd8cc738e928e5430ced">Letters from family, friends, and business associates of Asa Fish chiefly relating to ocean going trade, whaling, and sealing around the Cape of Good Hope and marine insurance. Also some material on politics in Connecticut.</abstract>
